"{\"uid\": \"newsus.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-29-Olympics-New-Zealand-s-Hayden-Wilde-on-Paris-triathlon-struggles-1vCAzniqnTy-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Williams  Copied  Organizers of Paris 2024 are hoping for better weather over the next few days, which would allow for the water quality of the River Seine to improve ahead of a triathlon competition set for Tuesday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heavy rain over the last 24 hours forced Sunday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s practice session to be canceled over safety concerns about the water.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it does not improve, the swim section will be dropped and the event will become a duathlon, made up of cycling and running.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN's Dan Williams spoke with New Zealand's Hayden Wilde about the issues facing the triathlon and on the possibility of reducing the competition to a biathlon.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Williams_(defensive_tackle)\", \"score\": 0.8704974784794591, \"rank\": 0.0743801652892524, \"text\": \"Dan Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Williams_(defen